trans-unit.source: LerpBlend can be useful to create advanced animation effects based on individual animation clips. For instance, given a player character,, lerp blending could be used to combine a walking animation clip with an injured animation clip based on a blend factor that increases the more the player gets injured. This would then allow with blend factor == 0 to have a non injured walking player, with blend factor == 1 a fully injured player, with blend factor == 0.5 a partially walking and injured player.
trans-unit.target: LerpBlend可用于基于单个动画剪辑创建高级动画效果。例如，在给定玩家角色的情况下，可以使用lerp混合将步行动画剪辑与受伤的动画剪辑结合起来，而混合因子会随着玩家受伤的增加而增加。然后，这将允许混合因子== 0的情况下有一名未受伤的步行运动员，混合因子== 1的情况下具有完全受伤的运动员，混合因子== 0.5的情况下具有部分步行和受伤的运动员。

trans-unit.source: FastBlur offers lower blur quality than GaussianBlur, but it is faster to render. The FastBlur effect softens the source content by blurring it with algorithm which uses the source content downscaling and bilinear filtering. Use this effect in situations where the source content is rapidly changing and the highest possible blur quality is not needed.
trans-unit.target: FastBlur提供的模糊质量低于GaussianBlur，但渲染速度更快。所述FastBlur效果通过与使用源内容缩减和双线性滤波算法模糊它软化的源内容。在源内容快速变化且不需要最高模糊质量的情况下，请使用此效果。

trans-unit.source: GammaAdjust is applied to each pixel according to the curve which is pre-defined as a power-law expression, where the property gamma is used as the reciprocal scaling exponent. Refer to the property documentation of gamma for more details.
trans-unit.target: GammaAdjust根据预定义为幂律表达式的曲线应用于每个像素，其中属性gamma用作倒数缩放指数。有关更多详细信息，请参考gamma的属性文档。

trans-unit.source: GaussianBlur effect softens the image by blurring it with an algorithm that uses the Gaussian function to calculate the effect. The effect produces higher quality than FastBlur, but is slower to render.
trans-unit.target: GaussianBlur效果通过使用高斯函数来计算效果的算法来模糊图像，从而使图像变软。该效果比FastBlur产生更高的质量，但渲染速度较慢。

trans-unit.source: HueSaturation is similar to the Colorize effect, but the hue and saturation property values are handled differently. The HueSaturation effect always shifts the hue, saturation, and lightness from the original, instead of setting them.
trans-unit.target: HueSaturation与Colorize效果相似，但是对hue和饱和度属性值的处理方式不同。“ 色相饱和度”效果始终会改变原始色相，饱和度和明暗度，而不是对其进行设置。

trans-unit.source: MaskedBlur effect softens the image by blurring it. The intensity of the blur can be controlled for each pixel using maskSource so that some parts of the source are blurred more than others.
trans-unit.target: MaskedBlur效果通过模糊图像来柔化图像。可以使用maskSource控制每个像素的模糊强度，以使源的某些部分比其他部分更模糊。

CheckDelegate inherits its API from ItemDelegate, which is inherited from AbstractButton. For instance, you can set text, and react to clicks using the AbstractButton API. The state of the check delegate can be set with the checked property.
trans-unit.target: CheckDelegate从ItemDelegate继承其API，ItemDelegate从AbstractButton继承。例如，您可以设置text，并使用AbstractButton API 对点击做出反应。可以使用checked属性设置检查委托的状态。

trans-unit.source: CheckDelegate presents an item delegate that can be toggled on (checked) or off (unchecked). Check delegates are typically used to select one or more options from a set of options in a list. For smaller sets of options, or for options that need to be uniquely identifiable, consider using CheckBox instead.
trans-unit.target: CheckDelegate提供了一个项目委托，可以将其打开（选中）或关闭（未选中）。检查委托通常用于从列表中的一组选项中选择一个或多个选项。对于较小的选项集或需要唯一标识的选项，请考虑使用CheckBox。

trans-unit.source: ComboBox can be made editable. An editable combo box auto-completes its text based on what is available in the model.
trans-unit.target: ComboBox可以设为可编辑的。可编辑的组合框会根据模型中可用的内容自动完成其文本。
ComboBox由背景，内容项，弹出窗口，指示器和委托组成。

trans-unit.source: ComboBox is a combined button and popup list. It provides a means of presenting a list of options to the user in a way that takes up the minimum amount of screen space.
trans-unit.target: ComboBox是组合的按钮和弹出列表。它提供了一种以占用最少屏幕空间的方式向用户显示选项列表的方法。

trans-unit.source: ComboBox is able to visualize standard data models that provide the modelData role:
trans-unit.target: ComboBox能够可视化提供 modelData 角色的标准数据模型：

trans-unit.source: ComboBox is populated with a data model. The data model is commonly a JavaScript array, a ListModel or an integer, but other types of data models are also supported.
trans-unit.target: ComboBox填充有数据模型。数据模型通常是JavaScript数组，ListModel或整数，但也支持其他类型的数据模型。

trans-unit.source: ComboBox is used to select a value from a static multiple-line drop-down list. It is not possible to add new values, and only one option can be selected.
trans-unit.target: ComboBox用于从静态多行下拉列表中选择一个值。无法添加新值，并且只能选择一个选项。

trans-unit.source: DelayButton consists of two visual items: background and content item.
DelayButton is a button that incorporates a delay before triggering an action. This delay prevents accidental presses.
trans-unit.target: DelayButton是在触发动作之前包含延迟的按钮。此延迟可防止意外按下。

trans-unit.source: DelayButton is a checkable button that incorporates a delay before the button becomes checked and the activated() signal is emitted. This delay prevents accidental presses.
trans-unit.target: DelayButton是一个可检查的按钮，其中包含在按钮被检查并发出Activate （）信号之前的延迟。此延迟可防止意外按下。

trans-unit.source: Dial is similar to a traditional dial knob that is found on devices such as stereos or industrial equipment.
trans-unit.target: 拨盘类似于立体声或工业设备等设备上的传统拨盘旋钮。
对话框，抽屉，菜单和工具提示

trans-unit.source: Drawer provides a swipe-based side panel, similar to those often used in touch interfaces to provide a central location for navigation.
trans-unit.target: 抽屉提供基于滑动的侧面板，类似于在触摸界面中经常使用的侧面板，以提供导航的中心位置。

trans-unit.source: Frame is used to layout a logical group of controls together, within a visual frame.
trans-unit.target: 框架用于在可视框架内将一组逻辑控件布局在一起。

trans-unit.source: GroupBox consists of two visual items: background and label.

GroupBox is used to layout a logical group of controls together, within a titled visual frame. GroupBox does not provide a layout of its own, but requires you to position its contents, for instance by creating a RowLayout or a ColumnLayout.
trans-unit.target: GroupBox用于在标题的可视框架内将一组逻辑控件布局在一起。GroupBox不提供自己的布局，但是需要您定位其内容，例如，通过创建RowLayout或ColumnLayout。

trans-unit.source: GroupBox is used to layout a logical group of controls together, within a titled visual frame.
trans-unit.target: GroupBox用于在标题的可视框架内将一组逻辑控件布局在一起。

trans-unit.source: ItemDelegate consists of two visual items: background and content item.
ItemDelegate inherits its API from AbstractButton. For instance, you can set text, display an icon, and react to clicks using the AbstractButton API.
trans-unit.target: ItemDelegate从AbstractButton继承其API 。例如，您可以使用AbstractButton API 设置文本，显示图标并对单击做出反应。

trans-unit.source: ItemDelegate presents a checkable control that can be pressed and clicked by the user.
trans-unit.target: ItemDelegate提供了一个可检查的控件，用户可以单击该控件。

trans-unit.source: ItemDelegate presents a standard view item. It can be used as a delegate in various views and controls, such as ListView and ComboBox.
trans-unit.target: ItemDelegate呈现标准视图项。它可以在各种视图和控件（例如ListView和ComboBox）中用作委托。

trans-unit.source: Menu control can be used for context menus; for example, after right-clicking. It can also be used for popup menus; for example, a menu that is shown after clicking a button.
trans-unit.target: 菜单控件可用于上下文菜单。例如，右键单击后。它也可以用于弹出菜单。例如，单击按钮后显示的菜单。

trans-unit.source: MenuBar can have a visual background item, and MenuBarItem consists of two visual items: background and content item.
trans-unit.target: MenuBar可以具有视觉背景项目，而MenuBarItem由两个视觉项目组成：background和content item。

trans-unit.source: MenuBar consists of drop-down menus, and is normally located at the top edge of the window.
trans-unit.target: MenuBar由下拉菜单组成，通常位于窗口的顶部边缘。

trans-unit.source: MenuBar control can be used for window menu bars.
MenuBarItem is an item in the MenuBar control. Each item in a menu bar:
trans-unit.target: MenuBarItem是MenuBar控件中的一个项目。菜单栏中的每个项目：

trans-unit.source: MenuBarItem is used as a default delegate type for MenuBar. Notice that it is not necessary to declare MenuBarItem instances by hand when using MenuBar. It is sufficient to declare Menu instances as children of the MenuBar and the respective items are created automatically.
trans-unit.target: MenuBarItem用作MenuBar的默认委托类型。请注意，使用MenuBar时无需手动声明MenuBarItem实例。将Menu实例声明为MenuBar的子代就足够了，并且自动创建了各个项目。

trans-unit.source: MenuBarItem presents a Menu within a MenuBar. The respective drop-down menu is shown when a MenuBarItem is triggered via keyboard, mouse, or touch.
trans-unit.target: MenuBarItem在MenuBar中显示一个菜单。当一个相应的下拉式菜单中示出检测MenuBarItem被触发经由键盘，鼠标或触摸。

trans-unit.source: MenuItem consists of four visual items: background, content item, indicator, and arrow.
MenuItem inherits its API from AbstractButton. For instance, you can set text and icon using the AbstractButton API.
trans-unit.target: MenuItem从AbstractButton继承其API 。例如，您可以使用AbstractButton API 设置文本和图标。

trans-unit.source: MenuItem is a convenience type that implements the AbstractButton API, providing a familiar way to respond to menu items being triggered, for example.
trans-unit.target: MenuItem是实现AbstractButton API的一种便利类型，例如，提供一种熟悉的方式来响应被触发的菜单项。
